Method Detail

getAtomicGrounding

public WSDLAtomicGrounding getAtomicGrounding(AtomicProcess process)
Description copied from interface: Grounding
Get the atomic process grounding defined for the given atomic process. If there are multiple groundings specified one of them is selected arbitrarily. Consider to use Grounding.getAtomicGroundings(AtomicProcess) instead.

Specified by:
getAtomicGrounding in interface Grounding<WSDLAtomicGrounding,java.lang.String>
Parameters:
process - The atomic process for which to get its atomic process grounding defined in this grounding.
Returns:
The atomic process grounding, or null if none is specified for the given process.
